Union Token has eof; operator symbol: u8 and precedence: u8.

To choose token flag: i1, giving Token.
Give match flag:
true gives Token.operator with symbol be 10 and precedence be 5;
false gives Token.eof;
otherwise gives Token.eof.

To main, giving i32.
Let token be choose token true.
Give match token:
Token.operator with symbol and precedence gives (symbol as i32) plus (precedence as i32);
otherwise gives 0.
